Question: Should the government provide free college education to everyone the same way it provides high school education? Explain your answer.
Answer:
Im not sure.  While i would love to have the government pay for my education i dont really see that much of a benefit for anyone other than low income families.  If the government had a program that only supported those families (with some restrictions to prevent fraud) then i would be entirely for it.  As long as the system doesnt get abused and taxpayers dollars arent wasted by people only partying and not studying i dont see a problem with it.